00:21.962 --> 00:24.772
Richard, wake up.

00:27.695 --> 00:29.391
It's late.

00:29.392 --> 00:32.670
Richard, this is not the day
for you to sleep in.

00:32.671 --> 00:33.633
Verna?

00:38.021 --> 00:40.415
How'd I get back here?

00:40.416 --> 00:42.110
Where else would you be?

00:46.237 --> 00:48.066
I escaped from here.

00:48.067 --> 00:49.729
I was headed for my friends.

00:49.730 --> 00:51.426
Richard, you haven't
left the palace

00:51.427 --> 00:53.125
since you came here
to be trained as a Wizard.

00:54.923 --> 00:56.552
No.

00:59.018 --> 01:00.814
This is a trick.

01:03.046 --> 01:04.977
You're suffering
from Lacna'Han.

01:07.643 --> 01:09.672
When Wizards near the end
of their training,

01:09.673 --> 01:11.502
they're sometimes
plagued by

01:11.503 --> 01:13.035
lost memories
and strange dreams.

01:13.036 --> 01:16.434
The intense concentration
required by their studies

01:16.435 --> 01:18.899
overwhelms their minds.

01:18.900 --> 01:21.231
It'll pass.

01:21.232 --> 01:23.197
Now get dressed.

01:23.198 --> 01:25.296
There's someone
who needs to see you.

01:33.997 --> 01:36.061
Kahlan?

